text: $60, 000 - $70, 000. Super. Located in Inner CBD. Full time opportunity with a growing company. Exciting opportunity with a well-established boutique property developer who are seeking an Office Administrator to support their construction team. This builder developer has a strong portfolio of luxury projects predominantly in residential although the company boasts a number of other successful results. This Administrator will ensure the smooth running of the offices based in Fortitude Valley, supporting the construction team and be the first point of contact. This is an exciting opportunity for someone who enjoys a fast-paced role and working for a progressive company. Reporting to the General Manager, responsibilities will include, but not limited to include: First point of contact for the construction team. Answering phone calls and managing inbox. Provide high-level administrative support to the construction team. Match purchase orders to invoices and assist with accounts. Order and maintain stationery and kitchen supplies. Additional general office administration. Previous experience in a similar role, with a positive attitude and thrive in a fast-paced environment. Beneficial to have worked within the construction or residential industry. This person will have excellent written and verbal communication skills, ability to multitask with high attention to detail. Proficient in Microsoft Suite i. e Outlook, Microsoft Word & Excel. A great opportunity for an Administrator looking to work within a high-end property developer located in Fortitude Valley. If you are a self-motivated & organised individual, please apply!
